Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.15,0:00:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 186 of the Penal Code\NA person who habitually gambles or bets shall be punished by hard labor for not more than 3 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.98,0:00:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,NEW YEAR'S ZUGAN
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He drew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But he needs to discard 1p or 5p against 3 riichis ...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one will ya cut, boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.88,0:01:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,YASU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,AKECHI
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.30,0:01:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,AKINA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.48,0:01:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.60,0:01:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.20,0:01:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ... see the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,B-boss!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the bloody hell happened to ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.97,0:01:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Suuankou tanki.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As dealer, that's 96000.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a whole different man!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely different from last year's Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,NEW YEAR'S EVE 1992
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.28,0:01:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,For juice, is grapefruit fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.36,0:02:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Daijoubu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.16,0:02:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shan't buy any New Year's soba noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Tonbee noodles!\N(TN: Sanuki udon, a popular Shikoku dish)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'm a stickler for tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's common for cup noodles to run out before New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.02,0:02:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,500 yen per cup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Toyotomi ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to eat those trashy cup noodles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.57,0:02:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you maybe cook me homemade soba yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They got a new wrapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get hungry, eat a lot of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shintarou's gone to his hometown, I wonder how he's doing ...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing mahjong no doubt!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.88,0:02:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that guy's got no brains for anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a single good thing's happened to me all year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, m-me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have the look of a lucklet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell your fortune for next year using my guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.84,0:03:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In '92 you were unlucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.52,0:03:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,However next year it will go well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa luckshit luckshit yeah yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he mean by this ...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What a load of bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.39,0:03:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, funny guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You guys still eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.11,0:03:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, let's play after we're done, hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to play already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.67,0:03:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously! Let's go, pick your seat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,EAST 1 TURN 8
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.43,0:03:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Crikey! Doragiri riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fodl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:04:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooly dooley!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What a bewt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.94,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,4p is safe, so cut 7p and wait on the dora which just passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a superb wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Cringe!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's piss-weak, mate, I'm spewin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, maybe ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.02,0:04:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If 7p passed you'd have won 6400!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.35,0:04:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't whisper so close to my ear, retard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.82,0:04:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty spiffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now cut 3m and with 9p it's riichi chun iipeikou for 5200! She'll be right, mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.16,0:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to push!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Piss-poor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If ya'd kept the chun ya'd have hit the 6p with riichi ippatsu chun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cutting chun for iipeikou nomi dama ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Pig's arse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.60,0:05:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Crikey! He's even breakin' his tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I overestimated ya, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,From today my new boss is Hayami!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No backseating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What d'ya mean by that!? Ya promised me you'd let me teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.49,0:05:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it myself, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no no no, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's dicey, mate, bloody dicey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.28,0:05:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.66,0:05:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi ippatsu chanta sanshoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.00,0:05:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneman, mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.64,0:05:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Akechi, what was ya hand, mate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.83,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a mentanpin 258m wait with sanshoku ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Many such cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Both 7p and 3m would have passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.44,0:05:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:06:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon! Pon! Sore pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.73,0:06:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,5p ... the dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Fold with suji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The cheaper out ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi ippatsu tanyao!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at -3200 in the shadowrealm ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.54,0:06:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This 5-shanten haipai will be this year's last ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This year's last riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Akemashite omedetou!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi ippatsu ittsuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.58,0:06:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.76,0:06:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi, I hope you'll do the needful this year too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Toyotomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ura suji ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All those dangerous tiles ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.72,0:07:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.26,0:07:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi tanyao pinfu iipeikou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy rigged ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.39,0:07:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not last year's Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wut? Shan't believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Toyotomi, deal in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi, huh ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ura suji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I have genbutsu ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I cut 4m on purpose!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.46,0:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because ...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.85,0:07:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm confident!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:07:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Matagi suji!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.74,0:08:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Suji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.47,0:08:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,3 times out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.91,0:08:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.41,0:08:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbutsu riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.44,0:08:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So confident! Those discards with this hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss's reincarnated into a chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The fortune telling was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wut?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi ippatsu tanyao!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.03,0:08:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya might flog Akechi and Tokugawa ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.51,0:08:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But until ya flog Miss Hayami ya aren't the dinky-di!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,TURN 10
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,DORA 6s
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Closed honitsu iishanten!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.80,0:08:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,She made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.81,0:08:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut 5s for 8s kanchan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Or 9s for 6s kanchan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.76,0:08:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But 6s is the dora ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No one will discard it ...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Push the haku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Pon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Crikey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The hatsu and chun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't been cut at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt this is daisangen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.97,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I shan't discard this ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fold with ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.42,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Haku dora 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nooo, you can't cut dora from that hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.77,0:09:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya ning-nong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.93,0:09:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,A new dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun rises on 1993, Toyotomi's Year 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.46,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Sanankou chanta honitsu hatsu chun ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.91,0:10:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! As expected of me boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.52,0:10:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ya're the only one in the green!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasu, -1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Akechi, -1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Akina, -1!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi, +3!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, cheers to you for today's game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Sole winner ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so trifling when you look back on it ...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.46,0:10:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Toyotomi, since you're the sole winner, why don't ya treat us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's New Year after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the calf steak, Koakuma spicy style!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have a large "fabula" with extra egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.50,0:10:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have the Sanzeno full course menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine if I wrap my laughin' gear round the same as Hayami?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And some pickles for me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.71,0:11:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus ended the turbulent year 1992 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and heading towards the dramatic climax, Toyotomi's year 1993 began!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.45,0:11:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Three months remain until Super Zugan's final episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And to you dear viewers, Happy New Year!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,East 4, South seat, 12th turn, 27800 points.\NTsumo 2p dora 7s
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,1p riichi\NTN: one of the 5p should be a 4p, see last frame
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wut? Riichi on turn 4 already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut 2p and call riichi with up to pinfu iipeikou dora 1 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,2p should pass ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.07,0:11:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No ... it's only turn 4 ...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's also possible to cut 1p genbutsu and go for tanyao!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha thinking about? Just cut something!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I can draw 34s for sanshoku ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But can I afford to slow my hand down that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.13,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.75,0:12:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,ONCE UPON A ZUGAN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! Stop it, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.75,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wut?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a go at the turtle too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.84,0:12:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you shouldn't bully animals ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.79,0:13:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I shan't let you abuse a helpless animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cocky guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.92,0:13:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, no match for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.01,0:13:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All talk and no bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tangs{\i0}! {\i1}Tangs{\i0} for {\i1}kelping{\i0} me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me {\i1}roe{\i0} you to the Dragon Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you {\i1}perch {\i0}yourself on my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.40,0:13:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dragon Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.87,0:13:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that where "the sea breams and flounders dance"?\N(TN: from the schoolbook song "Urashima Taro")
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.43,0:13:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And a {\i1}bonito{\i0} princess too, I hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dace{\i0} right, {\i1}chum!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.15,0:13:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanoshii!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Dragon Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsumo! Chiitoi {\i1}dorado{\i0} {\i1}dorado!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.56,0:14:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh {\i1}roe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sharks{\i0} to be you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a great many {\i1}minnows {\i0}and {\i1}whales{\i0} in that mahjong parlor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Otohime, I brought a customer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.91,0:14:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Otohime, working as manager of this establishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.17,0:14:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If you win at mahjong, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen these guys somewhere before ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wutcha yappin' on about? C'mon, chop chop, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shan't lose against minnows and whales ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi ippatsu dora dora bang bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I shan't give up on Otohime after just a mangan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Honitsu ippatsu haku dora dora! Baiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Riichi tanyao dora dora, as dealer that's 12000!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN PLAY ALONE AS WELL
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, your jewel box!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.80,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus, Urashima Taro's hair turned all white ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, such a big ii-pin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,From that ii-pin, a baby boy cute as a button was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And they gave him the inevitable name Zugantaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,15 YEARS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear goodness, he keeps eating through all our rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to him, we're in the red this month again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we get rid of him somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh ... I'm going to exterminate the demons and bring back a lot of treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.08,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Bloody oath, boss! We're countin' on ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And bring something back for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! Special point stick millet dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus Zugantaro left on his quest to exterminate the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.30,0:16:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are ya goin' in that hero getup?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.25,0:16:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be carrying some tasty stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hand it over, Zugantaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the precious millet dumplings my grandma gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I shan't give them to you lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well how about this ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We play mahjong, and if we win, we get the dumplings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I win?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.20,0:16:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be your retainers and follow you to Demon Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can lose against these animals ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.04,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanyao pinfu sanshoku, dealer's mangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.48,0:17:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it, I shan't lose against animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Scree! That's my wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinitsu pinfu dora 1, baiman!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.21,0:17:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This should pass ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ik ook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.62,0:17:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Suuankou monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's eat those dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you let me have just a bite ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.67,0:17:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What, you're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,100 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus they say that Zugantaro never got to Demon Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Red Lucklet! Little Red Lucklet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an errand for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring these tiles to your sick grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But these are mahjong tiles, Akina!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I'm your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.18,0:18:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And you might know this already, but ...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the Three Wolves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.96,0:18:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the sick grandmother here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.57,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, three cute boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.48,0:18:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got some spare time, why don't you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.39,0:18:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.85,0:18:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wut?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's obviously a 47s wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reading skills are no big deal ...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, 4s kan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron! Riichi tanyao ippatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.38,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.26,0:19:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a kan of 4s, so 8 ura. Sanbaiman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.26,0:19:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like we're in charge of this house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's here! Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to see you, grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.47,0:19:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.13,0:19:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, why are your hands so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to grab a lot of riichi sticks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.78,0:19:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma, why are your eyes so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:20:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,To look at your discards really well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And why is your mouth so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To say ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Toyotomi! Hey! Wake up, Toyotomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you even fall asleep playing mahjong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.09,0:20:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you even want to play seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.35,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out or bad things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.46,0:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.15,0:20:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! I can't let myself be misled by Akechi's discards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.24,0:20:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are all beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.85,0:20:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll avoid ippatsu and go for tanyao, cutting 1p!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.79,0:20:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Genbutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ron!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.23,0:20:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Akechi's genbutsu is a big hit for me! Junchan sanshoku pinfu dora dora!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.05,0:20:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Zugan ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk ...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlucky ...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus, Little Red Lucklet was all eaten up by the wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And they all lived happily ever after​.
